The paper deals with privacy-preserving video analytics, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of computer security (cs.CR), computer vision (cs.CV), multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), and privacy (cs.PR). However, since the paper focuses on the privacy aspect of video analytics, it is most likely to belong to the computer security (cs.CR) sub-category. The other sub-categories are also relevant because the paper involves techniques from computer vision, machine learning, and multimedia processing.
